thread.title: BRIEF-Southwest Airlines February Load Factor 81 Pct Vs 79 Pct Year Ago

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Southwest Airlines February Load Factor 81 Pct Vs 79 Pct Year Ago
text:
March 8 (Reuters) - Southwest Airlines Co:
* SOUTHWEST AIRLINES REPORTS FEBRUARY TRAFFIC * FEBRUARY LOAD FACTOR 81.0 PERCENT VERSUS 79.0 PERCENT YEAR AGO
* AVAILABLE SEAT MILES (ASMS) INCREASED 1.0 PERCENT TO 11.1 BILLION IN FEBRUARY 2018, COMPARED WITH FEBRUARY 2017 ASMS OF 11.0 BILLION
* FLEW 9.0 BILLION REVENUE PASSENGER MILES IN FEBRUARY 2018, AN INCREASE OF 3.5 PERCENT FROM 8.7 BILLION RPMS FLOWN IN FEBRUARY 2017 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
